<lb n="9"/>śānti-vācane <space/> Ihāmuttike <space/> dh<sic>ā</sic>mma-tthāṇe Etthaṅ-gāme <space/> Ādhivvaṇika-cara<lb break="no" n="10"/>ṇassa <space/> Āddhaka<surplus>|</surplus> bhālandāyaṇa-sagottesi<surplus>
